news.title: Over 50% rise in property tax collection in Ahmedabad
news.para: As per Ahmedabad Municipal Corporation’s (AMC) statement, the tax department collected Rs 328.42 crore in property tax this year against Rs 218.17 crore in the same period last year.

news.title: Kolkata: More Bowbazar buildings in zone of uncertainty
news.para: The team of experts from Jadavpur University, appointed by KMC to assess the affected buildings on Durga Pithuri Lane and the serpentine lanes off B B Ganguly Street have been visiting the site since Monday to ascertain the extent of damage suffered due to last Wednesday’s subsidence at the Metro construction site.

news.title: Gurugram: Why some residents are paying lakhs for new power connection
news.para: Of the over Rs 317 crore that the 13 private developers collectively owe to DHBVN for having failed to provide the much-needed power infrastructure in these 16 plotted colonies and 32 housing societies developed by them.
